parameters: Shopkeeper: "It's alright... Umi-chan has helped us out a lot..."

Shopkeeper: "I see... You must have your circumstances, Kru-san... This
child is Mia-chan. Umi-chan's child..."

Kru: "Is that so... No... I thought so when I saw her for the first time
yesterday."
Kru: "...Yes, nice to meet you. I'm your Toto."

Mia: "Stupid Toto--! Kaka and Mia have been... have been lonely all this
time!"
Mia: "I wanted to see you so much..."
Shopkeeper: "Kru-san... Were you looking for Umi-chan?"

Kru: "Yes... She disappeared from our village five years ago... and I've
been searching ever since..."

Kru: "But... Umi probably didn't want to see me... She wanted to live in
the present, putting our past behind her..."

Kru: "It can't be helped... There were various things... and I hurt Umi
deeply... It's my retribution..."

Shopkeeper: "This is Umi-chan's diary... It has entries about you, Kru-
san."

Shopkeeper: "I felt bad, but I ended up reading it... I think the truth
about you two is written here... Take a look for yourself..."
Shopkeeper: "Go on... I'll take care of Mia-chan here..."
Shopkeeper: "Make sure... you both come back together!"
